{"id": 2987, "genre": 1000, "title": "对你来说，“结婚”这件事最重要的前提是啥？", "description": "或者说，对你而言，婚姻的本质其实是啥？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 18699, "comment_count": 42, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190902182721zefWDcPqG5dFNaJC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5887, "title": "对你来说，“结婚”这件事最重要的前提是啥？", "content": "对你来说，婚姻当中的哪些事情是绝对不能省略的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 346041, "content": "跟爱的人在一起，感情有个寄托", "image": "img/option/option/20190903183058HzFgic7UIh0N9E5O.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346051, "content": "跟爱我的人在一起，可以照顾我", "image": "img/option/option/20190903184250yjXLFlPSrJ4mt9uo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346042, "content": "跟优秀的人在一起，让自己提升", "image": "img/option/option/20190903184437Ejd5NWtlR2KOCh13.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346048, "content": "两个人拥有/达成一致的价值观", "image": "img/option/option/20190903183233NOjfshEBtMdVL8lx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346044, "content": "价值观可以不一致，能互相陪伴就行", "image": "img/option/option/20190903183704W5XQHy8Az4EBkwR2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346049, "content": "互相享受性", "image": "img/option/option/20190903183328n9EWZHmJ5z36hajQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346046, "content": "一起带孩子，或者叫合作育儿", "image": "img/option/option/20190903184016u2hpiIY0B6RNGryz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346047, "content": "组成家庭港湾，跟对方一起承担生活中的各种风险", "image": "img/option/option/20190903183441wN84HfYxDXvd3psW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346045, "content": "分担工作和家务，两个人一起能做得更多", "image": "img/option/option/201909031838441AynHoXuszRDtiG6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346050, "content": "财务共享，但不一定是上交工资卡", "image": "img/option/option/20190903183752WndEiIlAKmrtUvBC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346097, "content": "都没有，并不想结婚", "image": "img/option/option/20190904185328Lob4YPkj1I2csUwe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}